>\n但如果2選1<br />\n我會揀HIMYM<br />\n<br />\n有時間可以考慮睇埋The Office (US version)<br />\n我覺得好笑過B99"},{"pid":"0ca68dee7020098860caf21b6c805f9172f2b703","tid":2453750,"uid":833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T17:51:18.000Z","msg":"兩年前開始追b99,睇到第五季斷左<br />\n<br />\n近排先開始睇返，依定睇到第七，唔想咁快完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人物刻劃極豐富<br />\n<br />\n每個人都可以係主角<br />\n<br />\n一集廿分鐘，同時有幾個故事<br />\n<br />\n節奏快，唔拖，搞笑<br />\n<br />\n記得當初第一集。睇intro 前既兩分鐘片段就已經迷上左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a2ec971d49707f50589267902133f1f8b7eb16","tid":2453750,"uid":33975,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T17:53:45.000Z","msg":"99 &gt; big bang = himym"},{"pid":"09486eb8c14daca6c5f6ae747047344409275813","tid":2453750,"uid":127244,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ad1ac4a42db33b1c991b74aa46d0dc9b662c2b08","tid":2453750,"uid":132030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T16:22:26.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲2套都睇過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T17:56:39.000Z","msg":"套套題材都唔同，點比呀, 煲曬佢咪得<br />\nModern family / the office 都好撚搞笑"},{"pid":"41f6f1f0c32030f7da140d5939eda51fd4264ce4","tid":2453750,"uid":367769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"09486eb8c14daca6c5f6ae747047344409275813","tid":2453750,"uid":127244,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ad1ac4a42db33b1c991b74aa46d0dc9b662c2b08","tid":2453750,"uid":132030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T16:22:26.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲2套都睇過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T17:56:39.000Z","msg":"套套題材都唔同，點比呀, 煲曬佢咪得<br />\nModern family / the office 都好撚搞笑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T18:01:07.000Z","msg":"冇錯 兩套都係出名好睇嘅sitcom 梗係唔好錯過睇曬佢就啱㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇完呢兩套可以睇埋其他好睇嘅<br />\n例如好多人講嘅the big bang theory、friends、the office、it crowd、2broke girls、arrested development<img src=\